=\"font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong>Raison:</strong>{leave_reason}</span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">Merci,</span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">Département des ressources humaines,</span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">{company_name}</span></p>','2026-02-05 05:36:41','2026-02-05 05:36:41'),(231,15,'he','New Leave Request','<p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong>נוֹשֵׂא:</strong> בקשת חופשה חדשה </span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">עוֹבֵד {employee_name} הגיש בקשה לחופשה. להלן הפרטים:</span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong>סוג לעזוב:</strong> {leave_type}</span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong>השאירו משך זמן:</strong> {leave_start_end_time}</span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong>לְנַמֵק:</strong>{leave_reason}</span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">תודה,</span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">מחלקת משאבי אנוש,</span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">{company_name}</span></p>','2026-02-05 05:36:41','2026-02-05 05:36:41'),(232,15,'it','New Leave Request','<p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong>Soggetto:</strong> Nuova richiesta di congedo </span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">Dipendente {employee_name} ha richiesto un congedo. Ecco i dettagli:</span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong>Lasciare il tipo:</strong> {leave_type}</span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong>Lasciare la durata:</strong> {leave_start_end_time}</span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong>Motivo:</strong>{leave_reason}</span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">Grazie,</span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">Dipartimento delle risorse umane,</span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">{company_name}</span></p>','2026-02-05 05:36:41','2026-02-05 05:36:41'),(233,15,'ja','New Leave Request','<p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong>主題:</strong> 新しい休暇リクエスト </span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">従業員 {employee_name} 休暇を申請しました。ここに詳細があります:</span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong>タイプを残します:</strong> {leave_type}</span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong>休暇期間:</strong> {leave_start_end_time}</span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong>理由:</strong>{leave_reason}</span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">ありがとう,</span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">HR部門,</span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">{company_name}</span></p>','2026-02-05 05:36:41','2026-02-05 05:36:41'),(234,15,'nl','New Leave Request','<p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong>Onderwerp:</strong> Nieuw verlofverzoek </span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">Medewerker {employee_name} heeft verlof aangevraagd. Hier zijn de details:</span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong>Laat het type:</strong> {leave_type}</span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong>De duur verlaat:</strong> {leave_start_end_time}</span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong>Reden:</strong>{leave_reason}</span></p>\n                    <p><span style=\"font-family: sans-serif;\">Bedankt,</span></p>\n                  